14: SensCutOffCont                        0.030 // Dfax cutoff for post-contingency [0.00 to 1.00]. Only used if SensCutOffMode1.  Otherwise uses SensCutoff for both base and cont.

 9: monCutOff                                50 // Max number times to report the same branch conting Violations

13: SensCutOffBase                        0.030 // Dfax cutoff for pre-contingency [0.00 to 1.00]. Only used if SensCutOffMode=1.  Otherwise uses SensCutoff for both base and cont.
14: SensCutOffCont                        0.030 // Dfax cutoff for post-contingency [0.00 to 1.00]. Only used if SensCutOffMode1.  Otherwise uses SensCutoff for both base and cont.
